Class SimpleConsoleEventBusListener

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BuckEventListener, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class SimpleConsoleEventBusListener
extends AbstractConsoleEventBusListener
    Implementation of AbstractConsoleEventBusListener for terminals that don't support ansi.
